    <h2>🌿 What Is a Moss Agate Wedding Ring?</h2>
    <p>Moss agate is a type of chalcedony known for its green inclusions that resemble moss, ferns, or natural landscapes. These inclusions are usually formed by iron or manganese, giving the stone its unmistakable earthy appearance.</p>

