    <h2>🧼 Care Tips: How to Keep Your Moss Agate Ring Looking Its Best</h2>
    <p>Moss agate is durable but not indestructible. It ranks 6.5–7 on the Mohs scale.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Avoid sharp impacts—don’t wear during heavy lifting or sports</li>
      <li>Clean with lukewarm water + mild soap (no ultrasonic cleaners)</li>
      <li>Store separately from harder stones to prevent scratches</li>
    </ul>

